TY  - JOUR
TI  - Telecommunications and the dialysis patient
PY  - 1999
PB  - Elsevier BV
SN  - 0272-6386
T2  - American Journal of Kidney Diseases
DO  - 10.1016/s0272-6386(99)70100-9
UR  - https://doi.org/10.1016/s0272-6386(99)70100-9
DA  - 1999-07-01
AU  - Winchester, James
LA  - en
VL  - 34
